A slim diner managed to consume an 8,000-calorie sandwich weighing almost half a stone in just 36 minutes.

James Brettell, 26, became the first person to finish the 'Gigantwich' in Southend-on-Sea, Essex, which comes complete with a huge side-portion of chips and a large dollop of coleslaw.

A UK strongman and competitive eaters are among 116 people who have all previously failed at eating the giant meal in the allotted 45-minute time limit.

